article_title: At 205,000 Strong, The Nurse Practitioner Will See You Now

article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen

og.description: As the health care workforce shifts to treat patients in less expensive primary care settings, the number of nurse practitioners has nearly doubled in the last decade to more 200,000, new data shows.
